{
  "stem": "10862.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had never heard of the word ghetto till the Warsaw Ghetto, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what they did-- the Jewish community was organizing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had organized a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And an order was simply put out that you have to move within a certain area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We moved to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my aunt lived there-- my aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a very well-to-do aunt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she had suggested that we move in with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and it just so happened the area where she was at was considered a part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And once they organized the ghetto, of course, the Jewish children were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My sisters all had to quit school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our whole life was disrupted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everything that we had-- you could only take with you whatever you can carry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everything, the furniture, whatever you had, everything had to be left behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You could not take anything with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And what they tried to do is tried to put in so many Jews into a certain square-- not square block.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was bigger than a square block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But that was mainly their objective, to put everybody together in one place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was very, very hard in the ghetto, very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the beginning, it wasn't so bad, because they were still giving out pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they had rations, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I only remembered carrying something on my back-- probably all-- the all clothes, whatever I had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And believe me, I did not have very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because as I said to you before, we were not a well-to-do family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we just carried on our backs whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have anything really special for me, nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
